1. A student is writing code to calculate 
the average of three numbers. 
Which of the following code segments 
will correctly assign the average 
of the variables num1, num2, and num3 
to the variable avg?

A. avg <- (num1 + num2 + num3) / 3
B. avg <- num1 + num2 + num3 / 3
C. avg <- (num1 + num2 + num3) * 0.3
D. avg <- 3 / (num1 + num2 + num3)

doMath(1,2)